      <h3>ABOUT US</h3>
      <p>Launched in March 2015 and based in San Mateo, California, DraperTV spreads the entrepreneurial mindset and stories from founders and leaders in Silicon Valley all across the world.<br><br>

      Whether you are a budding entrepreneur or change leader looking to start your first venture, a founder looking for guidance on your business, or interested in being more entrepreneurial wherever you are, we look forward to helping you build an entrepreneurial mindset with our collection of videos, events, and courses.
      </p>
